This is not the first time I've seen Tomino seemingly rush through something and have time skips all over (*cough* Brain Powerd). It makes you wonder what could have been had he had 50 episodes to work with, or even 43 like the original. That being said, I did enjoy G-Reco. Anyways anybody else feel this way?
